  "markdown": "# Aerchain DS — Design System Specification

> Clean SaaS design system with a purple/teal gradient identity.
> Theme: light | Inspiration: Linear, Vercel

---

## Colors

| Token | Hex | Name | Usage |
|-------|-----|------|-------|
| \`--primary\` | \`#8B5CF6\` | Primary Violet | Primary actions, highlights |
| \`--secondary\` | \`#06B6D4\` | Cyan | Accents, badges |
| \`--contentBg\` | \`#FAFAFA\` | Content Background | Page background |
| \`--cardBg\` | \`#FFFFFF\` | Card Background | Card surfaces |
| \`--cardBorder\` | \`#F0F0F0\` | Card Border | Card outlines |
| \`--sidebarBg\` | \`#F9F9FB\` | Sidebar Background | Navigation panel |
| \`--primaryLight\` | \`#F3F0FF\` | Primary Light | Tinted backgrounds |
| \`--textPrimary\` | \`#1F2937\` | Text Primary | Body copy, headings |
| \`--textSecondary\` | \`#6B7280\` | Text Secondary | Subheadings, captions |
| \`--textMuted\` | \`#9CA3AF\` | Text Muted | Placeholder, disabled |

## Gradients

| Name | CSS | Usage |
|------|-----|-------|
| Primary Gradient | \`linear-gradient(135deg, #8B5CF6 0%, #06B6D4 100%)\` | Primary buttons, hero accents |
| Header Wash | \`linear-gradient(120deg, #F3F0FF 0%, #E0F7FA 100%)\` | Page header background tint |

## Typography

- **Font Family:** \`'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif\`
- **Mono Family:** \`'JetBrains Mono', monospace\`
- **Google Fonts:** \`https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap\`

| Element | Size | Weight | Tracking | Notes |
|---------|------|--------|----------|-------|
| Display | 32px | 800 | normal | gradient |
| Heading 1 | 24px | 700 | normal |  |
| Body | 14px | 400 | normal |  |
| Caption | 11px | 500 | 0.04em | uppercase muted |
| Code | 13px | 400 | normal | mono |

## Spacing

| Token | Value |
|-------|-------|
| \`--sp-xs\` | \`4px\` |
| \`--sp-sm\` | \`8px\` |
| \`--sp-md\` | \`16px\` |
| \`--sp-lg\` | \`24px\` |
| \`--sp-xl\` | \`40px\` |

## Border Radius

| Token | Value | Usage |
|-------|-------|-------|
| \`--r-sm\` | \`8px\` | Badges, chips |
| \`--r-md\` | \`12px\` | Inputs, small cards |
| \`--r-lg\` | \`16px\` | Cards |
| \`--r-xl\` | \`20px\` | Modals, panels |
| \`--r-full\` | \`9999px\` | Pills, avatars |

## Shadows

| Name | CSS | Usage |
|------|-----|-------|
| card | \`0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.04)\` | Default card elevation |
| elevated | \`0 8px 32px rgba(139,92,246,0.12)\` | Hover or active card |
| input | \`0 0 0 3px rgba(139,92,246,0.15)\` | Focused input ring |

## Components

### Button
- Border Radius: \`100px\`
- Padding: \`10px 24px\`
- Font: \`13px\` / \`600\`
- **Primary**: bg \`linear-gradient(135deg,#8B5CF6,#06B6D4)\`, color \`#FFFFFF\`
- **Secondary**: bg \`#FFFFFF\`, color \`#1F2937\`, border \`1.5px solid #F0F0F0\`
- **Ghost**: bg \`transparent\`, color \`#8B5CF6\`

### Card
- Border Radius: \`16px\`
- Padding: \`24px\`
- Border: \`1px solid #F0F0F0\`
- Hover: shadow → \`0 8px 32px rgba(139,92,246,0.12)\`, transform: \`translateY(-2px)\`

### Input
- Border Radius: \`12px\`
- Padding: \`10px 14px\`
- Focus: border \`#8B5CF6\` + shadow \`0 0 0 3px rgba(139,92,246,0.15)\`

### Table
- Header: \`11px\` / \`600\` / \`uppercase\`
- Cell Padding: \`12px 16px\`
- Row Hover: \`#F9F9FB\`

### Sidebar
- Width: \`220px\`
- Active: bg \`#F3F0FF\`, color \`#8B5CF6\`

## Design Principles

1. Clarity over decoration — every visual element earns its place.
2. Gradient identity — the violet-to-cyan gradient is a consistent brand signal.
3. Subtle depth — light shadows and micro-borders create hierarchy without noise.

---

*Auto-generated by Aerchain Design Extractor*
",
