.type-specimen { padding: 16px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #F0F0F0; }
.type-specimen:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.type-meta { font-size: 11px; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; color: #9CA3AF; margin-top: 4px; }
.page-header { background: linear-gradient(120deg, #F3F0FF 0%, #E0F7FA 100%); border-radius: 20px; padding: 40px; margin-bottom: 48px; }
.flex-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page">
<div class="page-header">
  <h1 style="font-size:32px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:8px;">Aerchain DS</h1>
  <p style="font-size:15px;color:#6B7280;max-width:600px;">Clean SaaS design system with a purple/teal gradient identity.</p>
  <div style="margin-top:12px;font-size:12px;color:#9CA3AF;">Theme: light | Linear, Vercel</div>
</div>
<div class="section"><div class="section-title">Color Palette</div><div class="section-desc">All color tokens extracted from the design</div><div class="swatch-row"><div class="swatch light-text" style="background:#8B5CF6;"><span class="swatch-name">Primary Violet</span>#8B5CF6</div>
      <div class="swatch light-text" style="background:#06B6D4;"><span class="swatch-name">Cyan</span>#06B6D4</div>
      <div class="swatch dark-text" style="background:#FAFAFA;border:1px solid #E5E7EB;"><span class="swatch-name">Content Background</span>#FAFAFA</div>
      <div class="swatch dark-text" style="background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #E5E7EB;"><span class="swatch-name">Card Background</span>#FFFFFF</div>
      <div class="swatch dark-text" style="background:#F0F0F0;border:1px solid #E5E7EB;"><span class="swatch-name">Card Border</span>#F0F0F0</div>
      <div class="swatch dark-text" style="background:#F9F9FB;border:1px solid #E5E7EB;"><span class="swatch-name">Sidebar Background</span>#F9F9FB</div>
      <div class="swatch dark-text" style="background:#F3F0FF;border:1px solid #E5E7EB;"><span class="swatch-name">Primary Light</span>#F3F0FF</div>
      <div class="swatch light-text" style="background:#1F2937;"><span class="swatch-name">Text Primary</span>#1F2937</div>
      <div class="swatch light-text" style="background:#6B7280;"><span class="swatch-name">Text Secondary</span>#6B7280</div>
      <div class="swatch light-text" style="background:#9CA3AF;"><span class="swatch-name">Text Muted</span>#9CA3AF</div></div></div>
<div class="section"><div class="section-title">Gradients</div><div class="section-desc">Gradient definitions</div><div class="gradient-strip" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg, #8B5CF6 0%, #06B6D4 100%);">Primary Gradient — Primary buttons, hero accents</div>
    <div class="gradient-strip" style="background:linear-gradient(120deg, #F3F0FF 0%, #E0F7FA 100%);">Header Wash — Page header background tint</div></div>
<div class="section"><div class="section-title">Typography</div><div class="section-desc">Font: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif | Mono: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace</div><div class="sample-card"><div class="type-specimen">
      <div style="font-size:32px;font-weight:800;background:linear-gradient(135deg, #8B5CF6 0%, #06B6D4 100%);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;">Aerchain DS — Display</div>
      <div class="type-meta">32px / 800 — Display (gradient)</div>
    </div>
    <div class="type-specimen">
      <div style="font-size:24px;font-weight:700;">Aerchain DS — Heading 1</div>
      <div class="type-meta">24px / 700 — Heading 1</div>
    </div>
    <div class="type-specimen">
      <div style="font-size:14px;font-weight:400;">Aerchain DS — Body</div>
      <div class="type-meta">14px / 400 — Body</div>
    </div>
    <div class="type-specimen">
      <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:0.04em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#9CA3AF;">Aerchain DS — Caption</div>
      <div class="type-meta">11px / 500 / 0.04em tracking — Caption (uppercase muted)</div>
    </div>
    <div class="type-specimen">
      <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:400;font-family:'JetBrains Mono', monospace;">Aerchain DS — Code</div>
      <div class="type-meta">13px / 400 — Code (mono)</div>
    </div></div></div>
<div class="section"><div class="section-title">Border Radius</div><div class="section-desc">Radius scale</div><div class="flex-row"><div style="width:60px;height:50px;background:#F3F0FF;border:2px solid #DDD6FE;border-radius:8px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:10px;font-family:monospace;">8px</div>
        <div style="width:60px;height:50px;background:#F3F0FF;border:2px solid #DDD6FE;border-radius:12px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:10px;font-family:monospace;">12px</div>
        <div style="width:60px;height:50px;background:#F3F0FF;border:2px solid #DDD6FE;border-radius:16px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:10px;font-family:monospace;">16px</div>
        <div style="width:60px;height:50px;background:#F3F0FF;border:2px solid #DDD6FE;border-radius:20px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:10px;font-family:monospace;">20px</div>
        <div style="width:60px;height:50px;background:#F3F0FF;border:2px solid #DDD6FE;border-radius:9999px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:10px;font-family:monospace;">9999px</div></div></div>
<div class="section"><div class="section-title">Design Principles</div><div class="section-desc">Core rules that define this design system</div><div class="sample-card"><ol style="padding-left:20px;list-style:decimal;"><li style="padding:8px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #F0F0F0;font-size:13px;">Clarity over decoration — every visual element earns its place.</li>
      <li style="padding:8px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #F0F0F0;font-size:13px;">Gradient identity — the violet-to-cyan gradient is a consistent brand signal.</li>
      <li style="padding:8px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #F0F0F0;font-size:13px;">Subtle depth — light shadows and micro-borders create hierarchy without noise.</li></ol></div></div>
</div>
</body>
</html>"
`;

